  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Laparoscopic adhesiolysis has been used in treatment of chronic abdominal pain. There has
      been only one previous controlled study, that stated laparoscopy alone had the same benefits
      than laparoscopic adhesiolysis. The aim of this study is to compare laparoscopic adhesiolysis
      with a placebo-procedure in chronic abdominal pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
